attributes.additional_details: We demand that the Eating Disorder Services be inclusive of ARFID - as should be the basic human right of anyone suffering. We believe too many people are falling through the cracks in the system. We believe that ARFID individuals deserve equal rights to treatment and the chance to recover from this life-threatening disorder.
attributes.background: We think that everyone who needs it should be able to access treatment for ARFID. I think funding should be increased for the treatment of ARFID.
